    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know those numbers exist, but they don't make the physical pain go away. they just talk about \"coping,\" but how do you cope with a life that's nothing but a sensory nightmare? it feels so cruel that we're forced to just endure this forever. it feels less like \"living\" and more like just being punished. it's hard not to think that the only way to actually stop the punishment is to just... exit.",
